  "design_notes": "The medium chart mirrors the rhythmic rise and fall of the energy. We start with minimal steps in the intro, introduce light stream movements during S2, take a brief breather on the downbeat of bar 21, and step up the density with jumpstream/runningman patterns during the drops S4, S5, and S6. Holds are used to emphasize key melodic synth swells, maintaining a comfortable 10% hold ratio which keeps the pad-play feel casual but expressive.",
